against Christ, whose Storie is their shame: And albeit some
of them do make a shew of Christianitie: yet are they voide
of all feare of God, and of no religion at all: but let vs [$saide
G.$] leaue of speaking any furder of them at this time: and
at my comming backe from Sea I will make a great
<P E1V>
number of them be manifestly knowne to the world. [$With that
